Class HandleTripCommand

java.lang.Object
  command.Command
      command.HandleTripCommand

public class HandleTripCommand
extends Command

This class handles trips. Sends a request for taxi id and coordinates to all peers in its list. After 5 seconds it will collect all taxis relevant for the trip from the database. Calculate shortest path for relevant taxis and sort them. Then it sends a taxi offer to the closest taxi and deletes offered taxis from taxi list. Starts a 5 minute timer that checks if any of the offered taxi have accepted the trip. If the timer runs out and no taxis have accepted trip, it will send offers to the next 5 closest taxis. This continues until no more taxis are available in which case the trip is reset and added to the trips table again.
